==English==

===Etymology===
A reversed spelling of the English word [[murder]]. This word is most known from Stephen King's novel and/or movie ''The Shining''; however, it has now appeared in [[rap]] songs as well.

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/'rɛdrʌm/}}

====Homophones====
*[[red]] [[rum]]

===Noun===
'''redrum'''

# [[murder|Murder]].

====Quotations====
"One, I come with premeditated redrum..." Redman, "Do What Ya Feel", ''Muddy Waters'', 1996

